From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000084 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Codex <codex@openai.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jun 2026 00:55:00 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] misc: expand Fruit Jam usbhost RX capture

The Linux HCD path must be able to receive a complete full-speed data packet:
sync, PID, up to 64 payload bytes, and the trailing CRC16.  Keep enough packet
history for that full packet so enumeration and diagnostics do not truncate
larger HID/XInput descriptor responses.
---
 drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c b/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
index 111111111111..222222222222 100644
--- a/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
+++ b/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
@@ -60 +60 @@
-#define FJ_USBHOST_RX_BYTES_MAX		32u
+#define FJ_USBHOST_RX_BYTES_MAX		72u
-- 
2.39.5
